The templates in this directory create species
guide.

Actions in: W::W::Controller::Species

/species/guide         -> species_summary-all.tt2
/species/guide/SPECIES -> species_summary-individual.tt2

Widgets are under the "component" URL space:

/species/guide/component/overview         -> summary/overview.tt2
/species/guide/component/SPECIES/overview -> SPECIES/overview.tt2